snippet.title: HA/CK Classic | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Download links below.
HA/CK is a game inspired by puzzle games like Portal, HA/CK takes you within The System. Your aim is to beat the system in it's own game by hacking and travelling within.

Download: https://gampixi.itch.io/hack
https://gamejolt.com/games/hack/264757
HA/CK has GameJolt trophies and high scores.
